"A.P.241/12/1": "Ah, partner! Heard you helped get Yuki and Aurora back safe and sound. I owe ya."
"Though, they won't tell me anything about where they were, or what they were doing the whole time they were gone."
"You can't usually get Aurora to stop talking, but asking about it shuts her right up."
"I guess I should just be happy that they're back and everything... But I can't help but wonder."
"You're the one that saved them, right? In that case, you must know something about it..."
"Afin. Don't go poking your nose where it's not wanted."
"Trying to expose a maiden's secrets is in awfully bad taste, you know."
"Yuki, Aurora. Why are you being so bullheaded about this?"
"...Because it has nothing to do with you."

"It's not in very good taste to brush someone
who's worried about you off like that either... But I'm siding with Yu on this."
"Afin, even you've gotta have one or two things you'd really rather not remember, right?"
"It's the same here. We're not telling you because it'd be embarrassing."
"<%me>! Don't you go telling him what happened there either, no matter what!"
"Because it'd be embarrassing...? Why'd they go and make it sound even more interesting..."
